- A humanitarian effort to rescue users from typing essays into search bars. Complies with [common name conventions](/Wikipedia:COMMONNAME) – or as we call it, "the bare minimum of user empathy."  
- Pro tip: If you encounter a [piped link](/Wikipedia:Piped_link) here, assume someone either fought bureaucracy and won… or died trying.  

